Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:42.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}didn't shine for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.81,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}They're are miracles, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:48.30,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}And meetings and love,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.76,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}and seeds and buds,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:58.98,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}and even the fruits\Nthat are yet unripe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:02.64,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The orange colour
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:07.55,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}reminds me of a sunset\NI saw that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.58,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Our two shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:14.17,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}seemed like they were\Nholding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.45,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I wonder if someday the orange
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}will become sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:21.26,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Or will it wither away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.78,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I don't want to know\Nabout my future,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.01,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:30.35,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Sour...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:38.96,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it, but I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:47.11,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish would\Nturn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:50.19,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}is bathed in your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:53.93,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The ideals and dreams\Njust swell{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:56.84,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\fnGill Sans Std ExtraBold Display\b1\c&HBDCACF&}H{\r}ey, feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:00.78,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today, I tried eating an orange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:04.03,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}but it was so sour I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.50,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I couldn't leave it behind\Nlike I have been,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.09,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:13.42,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:16.87,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}It's Sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:20.41,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:25.47,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it... I love it.
