Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've raised Ryuuji-kun well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I-I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why my life was in "danger"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Listen, Ya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After falling for the fake voicemail that Taiga left,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko cried a lot and Grandpa scolded her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it's like Ya-chan is a child right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Families are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they haven't seen each other in about ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mum, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you spoiling Yasuko{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, there's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:14.58,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji-kun, hurry up and take your bath before the water gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you weren't married...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad ran away with another woman while I was pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though everyone told me to get an abortion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I couldn't protect you, and things broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Grandma say you raised me well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I'm a lot taller than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your back was really big when you were running...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So big that I didn't recognise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was also a little happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so afraid that you'd leave and never come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you left by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the last person who should say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but running away won't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it right in front of you, not in some place far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have to look at me... always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma said there's nothing wrong with sleeping in the same room, since we're going to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand how Yasuko became the way she is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-chan is laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm kind of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:05:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think running away and getting married will work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still want to have this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like if I don't do something here, things will break again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you and Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing broke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's okay for us to start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to run away to get married. Let's do it with everyone's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be best to receive everyone's blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you mean by "everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, Grandma, and your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will take a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we'll be happy anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not share our happiness with everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but before that, let's have a little rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I, Takasu Ryuuji, will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter, just say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can it not matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... will marry Aisaka Taiga{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, I don't want a vow yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this your idea in the first{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Since ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast to equal the tiger."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, even without a vow, we'll always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your breathing is all weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lips are cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll hurt if we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we kiss, it'll definitely hurt... a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a rough, dry wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it was really, really warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's cold, so let's do it once more{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just us two left,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now three people and a pet are coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you believed it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ya-chan would come if you lied,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then get back on good terms with Grandma and Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think she would,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't think she wouldn't either...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps families are like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan, you're coming over for dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family of three, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...{added - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.86,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot about you, Inko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go ahead, I'm going to go change my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't your parents be{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quick, since I'm making your favorite tonight; pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, what are you think{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously don't think about the consequen{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it ou{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, do you really hate me that mu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving, so do whatever you want! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that I would never be loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just making pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma taught me how to make some delicious taro rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ryuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but perhaps that was just an excuse for running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hidden and lonely, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I blamed my lack of confidence on my parents and my surroundings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ryuuji still loves me.{missing lines in background, TL plox - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to accept everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be proud of myself and love Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, Taiga didn't come over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, we can't understand if you don't tell us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What actually happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Taiga{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone, back to your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some bad news for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to family reasons, Aisaka-san is withdrawing from this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just received that message from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san will be going back to her mother's{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lie, right? It's a joke, right? She was forced, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't tell us or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your lives, you will all come to different crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whether you decide to stay where you are, or turn back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you still have to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san's decision may mean leaving you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a decision she tried her best to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's support her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days are so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all calling Aisaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Texting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should all take a good, hard look at your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.48,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.70,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go through if we all call at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Everyone, back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushie{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.00,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you clench your teeth for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Taiga transferring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takas{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I didn't want her to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd bring her back right now if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd ask her why she decided everything by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the only thing I can do right now is accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she learns how to be tidy at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A single sock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely find him for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That klutz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she forget these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember when I fell into the river{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was interrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, I even said it a few times to Kawashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can be really stupid sometimes too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomiya-kun, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I want to go, can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry for yesterday."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why are you telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I kind of understand what you said now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Taiga's text message!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Taiga replied to everyone who texted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it just a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that small dot a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're imagining things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's definitely a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she take a picture of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will protect you all from the faraway sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! She's not dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she means, "I'll try my best."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if the sky is pitch black, with nothing to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there will be stars shining somewhere out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep shining brighter and brighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely look better to people."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Taiga is kind of selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:17:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if that's the case, the sky will connect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we all shine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how far apart we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will definitely be able to see each other doing our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You overdid that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sent chills down my spine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the feeling of being young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I'll be happy if she's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of stars, someone caused a lot of trouble back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After taking the time to send us this, I think she'd be happy if we replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember putting it away with Ami-chan's tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think of these things to make others happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... You're amazing at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan's existence itself should be surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, before she became who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people loved her even though she caused trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was jealous of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she seems amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her body and heart are both so small and timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All she does is take whatever people throw at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't let anyone see her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same as {\i1}someone{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was seen through from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I hate myself when I pretend to be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm desperate to have others accept me for who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally understood after meeting Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's at least one person who understands me, I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it isn't love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just have to press here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please hurry up before my godlike power runs out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Takasu-kun, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast to equal the tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're not by my side right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leap through space and time, and always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These feelings will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Inko-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't this makeup a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should just use some softer colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inko-chan finally said his own name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be lonely once the seniors leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so cool and interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that our student council president, Kitamura-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be studying abroad in America after graduating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The president and the seniors made the cultural festival and the sports festival amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that the previous cultural festival was even more amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the legendary one where 2-C won everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It was all because of the Palmtop something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Palmtop Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who brings you good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person really existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the Palmtop Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to this school last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, she's Takasu-senpai's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in this world that nobody has seen yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something gentle, and very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you ever laid eyes on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why no one has ever seen it.{different from first ep - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world hid it so that no one could get their hands on it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, someday, someone will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one person who is destined to find it will be able to find it.{TLC plox, keep consistent with first ep - ryuu}
